	<item>
		<title>Pershing Square Holdings, Ltd. Announces Transactions in Own Shares &#8211; 21 July 2026</title>
		<link>https://pershingsquareholdings.com/pershing-square-holdings-ltd-announces-transactions-in-own-shares-21-july-2026/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 02:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Share Repurchases]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://pershingsquareholdings.com/pershing-square-holdings-ltd-announces-transactions-in-own-shares-21-july-2026/</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[LONDON&#8211;(BUSINESS WIRE)&#8211;&#160; Pershing Square Holdings, Ltd. (LN:PSH) (LN:PSHD) (“PSH”) today announced that it has purchased, through PSH’s agent, Jefferies International Limited (“Jefferies”), the following number of PSH’s Public Shares of no par value (ISIN Code: GG00BPFJTF46) (the &#8220;Shares&#8221;): Total Buyback &#8230;]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<style type="text/css">      .q4default .bwalignc { text-align: center; list-style-position: inside }           .q4default .bwalignl { text-align: left }           .q4default .bwblockalignc { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto }           .q4default .bwcellpmargin { margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px }           .q4default .bwleftsingle { border-left: solid black 1pt }           .q4default .bwpadl0 { padding-left: 0px }           .q4default .bwpadl1 { padding-left: 5px }           .q4default .bwrightsingle { border-right: solid black 1pt }           .q4default .bwsinglebottom { border-bottom: solid black 1pt }           .q4default .bwtablemarginb { margin-bottom: 10px }           .q4default .bwtopsingle { border-top: solid black 1pt }           .q4default .bwuline { text-decoration: underline }           .q4default .bwvertalignt { vertical-align: top }          </style>
<div class="q4default">
